skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: lexington vegan
des: List of vegetarian and vegan restaurant options in Lexington. Includes addresses, phone number, and brief descriptions which can be heard from Alexa, and read in the companion Alexa app. To enable, say "Alexa, enable Lexington Vegan." Then to use, simply say, "Alexa, ask Lexington Vegan for a fact."
